flowchart TB
    R1[Read README / 阅读 README] --> E[Inspect Environment / 检查环境]
    E --> B{Existing Runtime? / 是否已有运行时}

    B -->|Yes / 是| I[Incremental Integration / 增量接入]
    B -->|No / 否| N[New Setup Plan / 首次部署规划]

    I --> C1[Check dashboard, backend, frontend / 检查看板、后端、前端]
    N --> C2[Let AI propose minimal commands / 由 AI 生成最小执行命令]

    C1 --> S{Need script? / 是否需要脚本}
    C2 --> S

    S -->|Only when justified / 仅在明确需要时| SH[install.sh / install.ps1]
    S -->|No / 否| CM[Run minimal commands / 执行最小命令集]

    SH --> V[Validate services and dashboard / 验证服务与看板]
    CM --> V

    V --> G[Governed Task Flow Ready / 可进入治理链路]

    classDef start fill:#0b3b2e,stroke:#34d399,color:#eafff7,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef main fill:#0f172a,stroke:#60a5fa,color:#e5eefc,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef warn fill:#78350f,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#fff7ed,stroke-width:1.5px;
    class R1,G start;
    class E,I,N,C1,C2,CM,V main;
    class SH warn;
